:TITLE:
Member Information
:CONTENT:
The Member Information Form stores and updates information 
in the Northside EmPrep Member Database. 
This database is shared among members of the EmPrep group
and is intended to be used during emergencies, 
such as, earthquakes, evacuations, and  wildfires.
Also, the database will be useful for neighborhood security purposes.
<hr>
With this form you can store images of 
:LIST:
yourself -- selfie,
your housemates -- people and pets you live with,
your living structure -- view of front entrance so we can locate you by your address 
:ENDLIST:
<hr>
The following files available for download:
:LIST:
The current version of the EmPrep Member Database in a comma-separate-variable (.csv) spreadsheet form
:ENDLIST:
Additional files to download can be requested to be put on this list.


